  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13049165/lift_passes.jpg" alt="transferhero" data-udi="umb://media/008ff89395374b1da3516b685ab5de82" /></p>
<p>We are always keen to hit the slopes as soon as we can once we arrive at our chosen <a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">winter destination</a> for our much anticipated skiing holiday of the year.</p>
<p>To help you make the most of your next ski escape, we have compiled a list of some fantastic resorts with the shortest transfer times so your next ski holiday works for you:</p>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13099782/austria-1.jpg" alt="austriahero" data-udi="umb://media/c5f223cb5bac4e0aaf65850da9131199" /></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> ski holidays</h2>
<p> </p>
<table border="1" height="123" class="c-tabs-beta__content-table c-tabs-beta__content-table--row" style="width: 450px; height: 88px; float: left;">
<thead>
<tr style="height: 42px;">
<th style="width: 34px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Resort</th>
<th style="width: 89px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Transfer time</th>
<th style="width: 34px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Perfect for</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 31px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 31px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cdd4ba75e0044478e4b0e871b159997" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cdd4ba75e0044478e4b0e871b159997}" title="Alpbach">Alpbach</a></td>
<td style="width: 89px; height: 31px;">1 hour</td>
<td style="width: 34px; height: 31px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1}" title="Ski Holidays for Beginners">Beginner skiers</a></td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 21px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 21px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a></td>
<td style="width: 89px; height: 21px;">1 hour</td>
<td style="width: 34px; height: 21px;">Snowboarders</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 21px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 21px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a></td>
<td style="width: 89px; height: 21px;">30 minutes</td>
<td style="width: 34px; height: 21px;">Cross-country</td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"> </p>
<p> </p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a> is a popular and lively country, with plenty of ski resorts full of snowy pistes.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Well known for <a data-udi="umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079}" title="Apres Ski Holidays">après ski bars</a> and clubs but also for being welcoming and friendly, Austria has the perfect mix of all things ski. Full of traditional-style villages situated at the base of mountains, resorts here offer a good mix of local culture and vast ski terrains.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">With some of Austria's top ski resorts an hour or less away, you can’t deny it should be a top choice country for your next holiday if you are looking for a short transfer time.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13099784/france-1.jpg" alt="francehero" data-udi="umb://media/de54dec0c21644fca5d41927d62a32cc" /></p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a> ski holidays</h2>
<p> </p>
<table border="1" height="123" class="c-tabs-beta__content-table c-tabs-beta__content-table--row" style="width: 400px; height: 58px;">
<thead>
<tr style="height: 42px;">
<th style="width: 34px; height: 10px; text-align: center;">Resort</th>
<th style="width: 55px; height: 10px; text-align: center;">Transfer time</th>
<th style="width: 36px; height: 10px; text-align: center;">Perfect for</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 27px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 27px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/597c2d8b93354bef8c187c100894c3f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/597c2d8b93354bef8c187c100894c3f9}" title="La Clusaz">La Clusaz</a></td>
<td style="width: 55px; height: 27px;">1 hour</td>
<td style="width: 36px; height: 27px;">Intermediate skiers</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 21px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 21px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/957b02edc6d846dfb4b2a1b2d1a3222d}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a></td>
<td style="width: 55px; height: 21px;">1 hour 30 minutes</td>
<td style="width: 36px; height: 21px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">Family skiing</a></td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
<p style="text-align: left;">France is a favourite of any avid skier or <a data-udi="umb://document/13cca02f7ef4467cade8c8e89e68fe39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13cca02f7ef4467cade8c8e89e68fe39}" title="Snowboarding Holidays">snowboarder</a> and famously known for its many resorts that cater to the influx of winter sport enthusiasts.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">With high-standard accommodation options, bustling towns and quality food, <a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France">France</a> always lives up to its good reputation for a skiing holiday. Many of France's ski resorts are built at <a data-udi="umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55}" title="Insider's Guide: Best High Altitude Ski Resorts">high altitude</a> so are known for being snow-sure.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">With 2 of France’s popular resorts under 2 hours away via transfer, it is certainly worth adding to your ski wish list for next season.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13099785/italy-1.jpg" alt="italyhero" data-udi="umb://media/8e11c72c619f45b7ae31448f67c27848" /></p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a> ski holidays </h2>
<p> </p>
<table border="1" height="123" class="c-tabs-beta__content-table c-tabs-beta__content-table--row" style="width: 508px; height: 63px;">
<thead>
<tr style="height: 42px;">
<th style="width: 34px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Resort</th>
<th style="width: 114px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Transfer time</th>
<th style="width: 141px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Perfect for</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 27px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 27px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d'Oulx</a></td>
<td style="width: 114px; height: 27px;">1 hour 30 minutes</td>
<td style="width: 141px; height: 27px;">A <a data-udi="umb://document/b5cb9765812641b5bc1682861060520d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b5cb9765812641b5bc1682861060520d}" title="Couples Ski Holidays">couples</a> ski break</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 21px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 21px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50e23ca4eed84c0d9e0681e29aebcaea}" title="Sestriere">Sestriere</a></td>
<td style="width: 114px; height: 21px;">1 hour 30 minutes</td>
<td style="width: 141px; height: 21px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079}" title="Apres Ski Holidays">Après</a> ski holidays</td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902" href="/{localLink:umb://document/996aa9008def4ffe9a331c775cc97902}" title="Italy">Italy</a> offers the best of everything - skiing, cuisine and weather - the perfect combination for a winter getaway.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Italy always impresses and entices skiers and snowboarders back year after year. It offers a laid back environment, <a data-udi="umb://document/e9a3c77df19c4552878816499e7c956a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9a3c77df19c4552878816499e7c956a}" title="Insiders Guide: Where are the best ski resorts for foodies">long lunches</a> and perfect conditions out on the slopes. With resorts an 1 hour 30 minutes transfer away, it’s worth visiting this beautiful country.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13099786/swiss-1.jpg" alt="swisshero" data-udi="umb://media/3d9ce0884be540de869c81421c793822" /></p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> ski holidays </h2>
<p> </p>
<table border="1" height="123" class="c-tabs-beta__content-table c-tabs-beta__content-table--row" style="width: 484px; height: 64px;">
<thead>
<tr style="height: 42px;">
<th style="width: 34px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Resort</th>
<th style="width: 55px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Transfer time</th>
<th style="width: 36px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Perfect for</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 32px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 32px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b23ef1df250240c5a3657f721fdb96d0}" title="Klosters">Klosters</a></td>
<td style="width: 55px; height: 32px;">2 hours 30 minutes (train)</td>
<td style="width: 36px; height: 32px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb}" title="Skiing for Advanced">Advanced skiers</a></td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
<p style="text-align: left;">Switzerland is the jewel of skiing. Keen skiers appreciate all that <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a> has to offer, it is great for those who like to <a data-udi="umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/aee42e5bfb084fa984ce50ac300330fb}" title="Skiing for Advanced">challenge themselves</a> but also like to take in amazing mountain views.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">With a slightly longer transfer time than some other resorts, Switzerland does offer the ease of <a data-udi="umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5}" title="Ski holidays by train">train travel</a>, where you can spaciously sit back and relax and soak up the sights as you make your way to resort.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow u-text-center">
<p><img src="/media/13099783/canada-1.jpg" alt="canadahero" data-udi="umb://media/e5a36bc16beb45f9add6315e6f577d1d" /></p>
<h2><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">Canada</a> ski holidays</h2>
<p> </p>
<table border="1" height="123" class="c-tabs-beta__content-table c-tabs-beta__content-table--row" style="width: 462px; height: 49px;">
<thead>
<tr style="height: 42px;">
<th style="width: 34px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Resort</th>
<th style="width: 55px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Transfer time</th>
<th style="width: 36px; height: 15px; text-align: center;">Perfect for</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 34px; text-align: center;">
<td style="width: 34px; height: 34px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc094a7f49b04e9a845adc78e3c77f10}" title="Mont Tremblant">Mont Tremblant</a></td>
<td style="width: 55px; height: 34px;">1 hour 30 minutes</td>
<td style="width: 36px; height: 34px;"><a data-udi="umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/828e4c33a3674f48b9358960a2eb57bb}" title="Group Ski Holidays">Group holiday</a></td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8889d8c0e844cde8208727a22b5dfd3}" title="Canada">Canada</a> is on most skiers' bucket list destinations and we can see why. Full of Canadian charm, friendly welcomes, terrains and landscapes like no other - it's a skier's dream.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Resorts cover large areas to keep you busy for a week or more and always cater for any skier or snowboarder ability level, meaning it is ideal for everyone who loves the mountains. With lively cafes, friendly bars and homely restaurants, Canada knows how to host a hungry skier after a busy day exploring.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Yes, Canada has a longer flight time than European destinations, but the transfer times still rival places such as Italy and France.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
